#. Tag: title
#: quick.docbook:3
#, no-c-format
msgid "Quick Tour"
msgstr "Hitri ogled"

#. Tag: title
#: quick.docbook:6
#, no-c-format
msgid "Introduction"
msgstr "Uvod"

#. Tag: para
#: quick.docbook:8
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&ktechlab; is an IDE for electronic circuits and microcontrollers. It can "
"perform simulation a variety of components (logic, integrated, linear, "
"nonlinear and reactive), simulation and debugging of PIC microcontrollers "
"via gpsim, and comes with its own closely-linked and complementary high "
"level languages: &flowcode; and &microbe;."
msgstr ""
"&ktechlab; je IDE za elektronska vezja in mikrokrmilnikov. Izvaja lahko "
"simulacijo različnih komponent (logičnih, integriranih, linearnih, "
"nelinearnih in reaktivnih), simulacijo in razhroščevanje mikrokrmilnikov PIC "
"prek gpsim in prihaja z lastnimi tesno povezanimi in komplementarnimi jeziki "
"na visoki ravni: &flowcode; in &microbe;."

#. Tag: para
#: quick.docbook:10
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"It has been designed to be as easy to use and unintrusive as possible; all "
"components and FlowParts have context sensitive help, and simulating "
"electronics is as simple as dragging components onto the work area and "
"creating connectors that autoroute themselves between their pins. &flowcode; "
"allows users new to PICs to instantly create their own programs, while the "
"electronic simulation allows stepping through a PIC's assembly program "
"inside a circuit."
msgstr ""
"Zasnovan je tako, da je čim bolj enostaven za uporabo in nevsiljiv; vse "
"komponente in FlowParts imajo kontekstno občutljivo pomoč, simulacija "
"elektronike pa je tako preprosta kot vlečenje komponent na delovno območje "
"in ustvarjanje konektorjev, ki se samodejno usmerijo med svojimi nožicami. "
"&flowcode; omogoča uporabnikom, ki se šele spoznavajo s PIC-ji, da takoj "
"ustvarijo lastne programe, medtem ko elektronska simulacija omogoča "
"korakanje skozi program za zbirnik PIC-ja znotraj vezja."

#. Tag: title
#: quick.docbook:14
#, no-c-format
msgid "Documents"
msgstr "Dokumenti"

#. Tag: para
#: quick.docbook:15
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To get started in &ktechlab;, you will need to create a new document, whose "
"type will depend on your task:"
msgstr ""
"Če želite začeti uporabljati &ktechlab;, boste morali ustvariti nov "
"dokument, katerega vrsta bo odvisna od vaše naloge:"

#. Tag: para
#: quick.docbook:18
#, no-c-format
msgid "&flowcode; Document - Construct a PIC program via flowcharting."
msgstr "&flowcode; Dokument - Izdelajte program PIC prek diagrama poteka."

#. Tag: para
#: quick.docbook:19
#, no-c-format
msgid "Circuit Document - Simulate electronics circuits and microcontrollers."
msgstr "Circuit Document – Simulirajte elektronska vezja in mikrokrmilnike."

#. Tag: para
#: quick.docbook:20
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&microbe; Document - High level language for PICs, also used by &flowcode; "
"to generate assembly."
msgstr ""
"&microbe; Dokument - jezik visoke ravni za PIC, ki ga uporablja tudi "
"&flowcode; za ustvarjanje zbirnika."

#. Tag: para
#: quick.docbook:21
#, no-c-format
msgid "Assembly Document - Start writing a PIC assembly program."
msgstr "Dokument za sestavljanje - Začnite pisati program zbirnika za PIC."

#. Tag: para
#: quick.docbook:24
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&ktechlab; uses a Document-View model, in that the Document logic is "
"completely separate from open views of the document. This allows several "
"views of the same file."
msgstr ""
"&ktechlab; uporablja model Document-View, tako da je logika dokumenta "
"popolnoma ločena od odprtih pogledov dokumenta. To omogoča več ogledov iste "
"datoteke."

#. Tag: para
#: quick.docbook:26
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"On creating a new document, the view is created in a separate tab. Each tab "
"can support any number of views, tiled in any arbitrary pattern. This "
"allows, for example, simulating a PIC program in circuit, while stepping "
"through the program in an assembly document in the same tab."
msgstr ""
"Ko ustvarite nov dokument, se pogled ustvari v ločenem zavihku. Vsak zavihek "
"lahko podpira poljubno število pogledov, razporejenih v poljuben vzorec. To "
"omogoča, na primer, simulacijo programa PIC v vezju, medtem ko korak po "
"programu v dokumentu zbirnika v istem zavihku."

#. Tag: para
#: quick.docbook:28
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The contents of tabs can be duplicated by dragging the tab to an empty area "
"on the tab bar. They can be inserted into an existing tab by dragging it "
"onto that tab."
msgstr ""
"Vsebino zavihkov lahko podvojite tako, da povlečete zavihek na prazno "
"območje v vrstici z zavihki. Lahko jih vstavite v obstoječi zavihek tako, da "
"jih povlečete na ta zavihek."

#. Tag: para
#: quick.docbook:30
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Detailed instructions on the above documents can be found in their own "
"respective chapters."
msgstr ""
"Podrobna navodila o zgornjih dokumentih najdete v posameznih poglavjih."

#. Tag: title
#: quick.docbook:34
#, no-c-format
msgid "Drawing"
msgstr "Risanje"

#. Tag: para
#: quick.docbook:36
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In Circuit and &flowcode; documents, there are several drawing tools "
"available, including text. These are available by clicking on the paintbrush "
"icon in the toolbar. To draw, drag the mouse to form either a shape or a "
"line appropriate to the drawing tool in use."
msgstr ""
"V Circuit in &flowcode; dokumentih je na voljo več orodij za risanje, "
"vključno z besedilom. Te so na voljo s klikom na ikono čopiča v orodni "
"vrstici. Za risanje povlecite miško, da oblikujete obliko ali črto, ki "
"ustreza uporabljenemu risalnemu orodju."

#. Tag: para
#: quick.docbook:38
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When a drawing is selected, it can be resized by dragging its handles. "
"Holding down &Shift; while dragging will snap the handle to the underlying "
"grid. Each tool has basic options accessible from the toolbar, such as "
"colors. There are also more advanced options found in the <guilabel>Item "
"Editor</guilabel> sidebar, such as line and cap styles."
msgstr ""
"Ko je risba izbrana, ji lahko spremenite velikost tako, da povlečete njene "
"ročke. Držite &Shift; med vlečenjem se bo ročka zaskočila na spodnjo mrežo. "
"Vsako orodje ima osnovne možnosti, ki so na voljo v orodni vrstici, kot so "
"barve. V stranski vrstici <guilabel>Urejevalnik elementov</guilabel> so na "
"voljo tudi naprednejše možnosti, kot so slogi črt in kapic."
